  "description": "The first complete private-sector post-scarcity economic operating system. NUPA is a finished, ready-to-implement economic engine that solves seven interlocking crises at zero taxpayer cost: settles the 160-year 1865 Freedmen debt through private revenue; restores genuine economic sovereignty to Tribal Nations; creates a market-based Fixed Cost Arbitrage firewall that makes human labor cheaper than automation; converts 24 million acres of dormant BLM land into a self-funding infinite wealth engine; restores U.S. soft power globally by eliminating any credible argument of moral bankruptcy or moral hypocrisy; potentially advances human civilization by one full point on the Kardashev scale; and entirely dissolves the concept of a New World Order or shadow state by transparently aligning every major interest. NUPA operates through radical alignment of interests: everyone benefits. Peace becomes more profitable than war. If implemented, NUPA delivers the NUPA Legacy — 10 World-Changing Achievements: eliminating the national debt for $0.00, ending the era of resource wars, engineering a firewall against the AI apocalypse, settling 160 years of broken promises, restoring stewardship after 400 years to sovereign nations, vaporizing centralized overreach (anti-NWO), triggering the NUPA Baby Boom, checkmating the United States Congress, creating a mechanism to end poverty, and designing an infinite-performance income for life. NUPALTA is a non-federal land holdings agency and the independent entity responsible for the Verification Assistance Program (VAP). The federal government cannot interfere with this private census program. VAP Phase 2 uses Forensic Lineage Verification (FLV) — phenotype is legally and scientifically irrelevant. The human labor preference in Fixed Cost Arbitrage is open to every American.",
